title: Doutores
body: The following individuals received their doctorates from the University of Coimbra: Antonio da Gama (law), Fr. Francisco de Santa Teresa (theology), João Antonio Monteiro (philosophy), Viturio Lopes Rocha (mathematics), João Francisco de Oliveira (medicine), José Ferreira Pestana (mathematics), José Manuel da Veiga (law), Justino Antonio de Freitas (law), Jacinto Antonio de Sousa (philosophy), Aires de Ornelas de Vasconcelos (theology), Antonio João de França Bettencourt (theology), and Augusto Arzila da Fonseca (mathematics). (See each of these names for more details).
